Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others arrived at Zou,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.45,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,an island where their new \Nadventure will take place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:57.73,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This enormous island,\Nwhich is as high as the clouds, is,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as its name suggests, a zou (elephant) \Nthat has been alive for a millennium.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was hidden in the \Ngiant Whale Tree was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That red stone is called a Road Ponegliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kozuki Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were they the ones who made all \Nthose Ponegliffs in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the shogun of the Land of Wano\Nand the pirate Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Kaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was your master executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have been captured and targeted\Nbecause of that, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.\NYou could say it's a cardinal sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:05:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous {\i1}daimyo{\i0} - Kozuki Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...traveled to the last island Raftel\Nwith the King of the Pirates - Gol D. Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and witnessed the secret of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke's father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...went to Raftel with Gold Roger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Vow Between Two Men!\NLuffy and Kozuki Momonosuke!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your father one of \Nthe Pirate King's crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo's father was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm asking you, Momo!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He witnessed the secret of the world?\NProbably, with Rayleigh-{\i1}san{\i0} too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. We know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We learned the entirety of history.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The entirety of history...\NEven the 100-Year Void.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The 100-Year Void.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a century-long gap in \Nthe history of the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:41.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that mysteriously dark period,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they say the World Government \Nwas established.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since then, they have been ruling \Nthe world for eight centuries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The World Government strictly prohibits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...searching for the truth about\Nthe 100-Year Void.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happened in that century...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is said to be revealed\Nby reading the Ponegliffs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the past, in Ohara, the holy land \Nof archaeology where Robin is from,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Professor Clover was studying the Ponegliffs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to unearth the secret of the 100-Year Void.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he was wiped off the face of the earth\Nalong with all the Ohara people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything that relates to the 100-Year Void\Nincluding that incident has been...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...smothered by the World Government.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do they want to keep a tight lid\Non the history of the 100-Year Void?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even those who know about the secret\Nkeep their mouths closed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get the secret of \Nthe world out of you retainers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo and Caesar\Nwho were tied to Kaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were trying to catch you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you guys know the secret of the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Actually we don't know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} didn't want to\Nburden us with the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but even if we knew it,\Nwe wouldn't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we know or not,\Nwe'll keep being hunted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, the only option we have is to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we are defeated soldiers,\Nwe accept our disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and survive to this day for one reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because of Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s words\Nthat are etched in our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words are the reason we live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he left behind \Nwere just one phrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Open up the Land of Wano!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean by "open up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Land of Wano is closed off to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means no one's allowed \Nto leave the country
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or enter from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if they open up, that means\Nthey'll interact with other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity that, although we
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should have been shields\Nfor our master Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were saved by him instead\Nand we brought shame to ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we have to do now is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to put our lives on the \Nline and avenge our master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to kill the shogun \Nwho stole the Land of Wano
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and open the closed country to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Land of Wano is almost \Nentirely under the control
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the shogun and Kaido who've joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends are trying to \Nmuster dissidents there now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're still vastly outnumbered by\Nthe enemy's great army!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no chance to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's happening there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, to look for someone \Nwho will fight with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we set out to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we were heading for Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because to fight against the Beast Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we surely needed the help of \NMinks, our closest allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Kozuki Clan and the Minks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have a special bond from way back,\Nwhich means whatever happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll share the same fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than anything, the dog and I are\NOden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s direct retainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the day Raizo arrived here,\Nall of our warriors were prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when we actually fought,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it turned out like this against Jack's unit\Nwhich was just a part of Kaido's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! But that's because they \Nused that dirty weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one could've expected\Nthey'd use the poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were a judge to call foul and we'd win,\Nmaybe that would work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how dirty they play,\Nthis is our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we won't let it happen again!\NWe won't repeat the same failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an ace up our sleeve too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fight again, we'll show them \Nthe true power of the Mink Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We're not gonna just back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take your injury more seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you won't be able \Nto exercise that true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No drinking until you're fully recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No baths either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have a favor to ask, Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you too, Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's presumptuous of me to ask \Nyou a favor after you saved my life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've been impressed by\Nhow strong you guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we are fated to share the same purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will you help us fight to kill\Nthe shogun of the Land of Wano
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Emperor Kaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm begging you, Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yes! Who can ask for more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those samurai and the Minks!\NThey'll be a big help for us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were gonna fight Kaido sooner or later!\NWe gotta jump at this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even have a ninja, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! We've been traveling together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me you're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it!\NWe have to join hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment! Forget about what he said!\NWe'll teach him a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, think again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will make you less of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Luffy has a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...negotiate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just a figurehead, Momo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! He's only a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were an important person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a leader of these \Ngreat men, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna just cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you make him cry like that?!\NDon't be harsh to an eight-year old!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}. Generally, heirs \Ndon't necessarily stand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on their feet until they're fully grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If adults assist them properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Momonosuke-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, come here, Momo-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for what our stupid \Ncaptain said to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't see it all!\NAnd that's how the world is, Momonosuke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ready the flaming arrows!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run! There must be a way out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a foolish lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was an enemy to my parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed my mother too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to grow up\Nand become strong quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and avenge my father and mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect all my retainers too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough to know that you feel that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-{\i1}gara{\i0} got older and weepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because my body's still small,\NI can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have Kaido's head though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing it wrong!\NYou gotta grab tight! Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With more energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But I am grabbing your hand...\N--No, do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. This is how it \Nshould be.　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our leaders are bonded! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have to ask me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's cool, right?\N--Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to reflect on what we were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were treating him as a child\Nbut he is the head of the Kozuki Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were forgetting about that\Nand thinking we have to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though that was too harsh\Non an eight-year old,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one treats Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}\Nas a whole man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know why you guys admire him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Guys! Gather up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our objective is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to kick Emperor Kaido's butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Ninja-Pirate-Mink-Samurai Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is "Ninja" necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:27.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In their early days, Dogstorm and Cat Viper
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,set out to sea, led by Kozuki Oden!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:32.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When their historic ties to\Nthe legendary men
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:35.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who created an era come to light,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the road to the Great Treasure of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:40.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece will be\Nshown to the Straw Hats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Legendary Journey!\NThe Dog and the Cat and the Pirate King!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:52.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
